{"tid":2224651,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"HKPOPO又一力作 驚曱Sir • 遇淋愈強","createTime":"2020-09-30T16:09:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T16:34:31.000Z","uid":278154,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b33ed4a12872979227d52fbb5f0c9b84f07bebaf","tid":2224651,"uid":278154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T16:09:32.000Z","msg":"【小虎Sir &bull; 遇強愈強】<br />\n<br />\n小虎於去年10月1日執勤期間，被暴徒用腐蝕性液體襲擊引致嚴重創傷，其後接受多次清創、植皮及拆釘手術。右手傷口植皮後，曾經打上了超過200顆釘子。除了醫療上的協助，警隊亦為小虎及其家人在福利上作支援。<br />\n<br />\n今日（9月29日），屯門警區管理層透過視像通訊，跟進小虎近況。嚴重的創傷雖為小虎帶來苦楚，但小虎從未氣餒，憑着不屈的精神抵抗漫長療程。<br />\n<br />\n小虎藉此機會衷心感謝警隊及同袍一直以來的關心，並勉勵大家不忘初心，竭力保護市民，維持社會秩序。<br />\n<br />\n#忠誠勇毅<br />\n#遇強愈強<br />\n#早日康復<br />\n#戰勝痛楚<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6o6DuqW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6o6DuqW.jpg&h=1af72ead&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sg8KpZh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsg8KpZh.jpg&h=4547d56f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kPNZYji.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkPNZYji.jpg&h=9f7acb0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n多謝手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de44c278e061e7fc48c04f48e06b6a5e7ab4792a","tid":2224651,"uid":231583,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T16:10:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a3c22913f17dafaccc05824fa1448a17a68bd89b","tid":2224651,"uid":25858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"de44c278e061e7fc48c04f48e06b6a5e7ab4792a","tid":2224651,"uid":231583,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T16:10:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T16:11:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/